				Was thinking - If you were to open up all PvP, but put heavy penalties on doing it (Level Loss, Instant Guard Swarm, etc.), but had a specialized assassins guild or a Rogue Specialty of Assassin, and had to pay a HUGE amount of money to have it done (With penalty of some kind).  It would, in my opinion, add to the realism of the game.   <br>  <br> For example, 11th lvl Wiz offs a 3rd lvl warrior <br>  <br> 11th lvl wiz is now a 9th lvl wiz, with guards chasing him on site, if caught (Killed), Wiz gets throuwn into Jail for 2 real weeks (not game weeks).  The Wiz has to leave the zone, outside the zone, he is fine.  Can't go back for an extended period of time til the guards 'forget'. <br>  <br> What do U think??		

